**Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3G - Issue of Performance Rights):**  

- **Security Issuance:** 67,050,000 unquoted performance rights (CY5AJ) issued on 11/07/2025.  
- **Recipients:**  
  - **Directors/KMP:**  
    - David Southam (12M), Ernest Mast (12M), Kevin Tomlinson (5M), Brent Omland (3M), Raymond Shorrocks (3M), Mario Stifano (3M), Carl Travaglini (2.25M).  
  - **Employees/Consultants:** 29.05M issued under Listing Rule 7.2 Exception 13 (no shareholder approval required).  
- **Total Performance Rights Outstanding:** 87,978,809 CY5AJ.  
- **Ordinary Shares Outstanding:** 1,063,262,178 (CY5).  

**Material Impact:** Dilutive issuance to KMP/employees; no immediate liquidity impact (unquoted rights). Terms accessible via provided [URL](https://cdn-api.markitdigital.com/apiman-gateway/ASX/asx-research/1.0/file/2924-02936427-6A1260151).
